  "body": "### What's your issue about?\r\n\r\nCurrently we output the whole stack trace when any vyper syntax error or exception occurs.\r\nWith vyper entering beta, the time has come to supress the trace and return cleaner error messages.\r\n\r\nFull tracebacks should still be toggleable, vir the vyper binary. But by default the full trace (for the binary) should not be seen.\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed?\r\n\r\nsee `vyper/excpetions.py` and `bin/vyper`.\r\n\r\n#### Cute Animal Picture\r\n\r\n![](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/824194/40068398-bff97fe6-5825-11e8-827d-8b7dbc6cfbe4.png)\r\n",
